dmca.title: Google Images Child Pornography Complaint
dmca.body:
Image Received: 
Subject: Google Images Child Pornography Complaint
From: "Shantal Rands" 
On October 12, 2006 Google received notice of an image containing
child pornography in our search results. We removed this image and
reported it to NCMEC.


(ImageID 8357)
